          "slidecontent": "• Regulations like the UK's Online Safety Act and GDPR set legal limits on how AI can target and profile users\n• Consumers have the right to opt out of personalised advertising in many contexts\n• Transparency matters\n• Advertisers must disclose when AI is being used to generate or personalise content\n• Independent audits can help identify bias or manipulation in automated ad systems\n• Clear complaint and redress mechanisms give consumers a way to challenge harmful or misleading AI-driven ads"
