          "slidecontent": "• AI can target adverts with striking precision, using your data to shape what you see and when\n• Bias in training data leads to biased outcomes, often without anyone intending it\n• Personalisation is not neutral\n• Emotional manipulation in AI-generated messaging is a real and growing concern\n• Always ask who benefits when an advert feels unusually relevant or persuasive\n• As a next step, review the targeting settings on one platform you use regularly and consider what data you have shared"
